---
title: Ultimate Double Haloumi & Avocado Burger with Fries & Roast Tomato Salsa
description: Elevate your burger experience with our halumi and avocado burger, where pan-fried haloumi meets creamy avocado for a delightful texture contrast. Accompanied by a side of crisp golden fries and a roast tomato salsa, this burger delivers a symphony of flavours for an unparalleled experience.
